    <title>My Art Hobby Project</title>
    <introduction>
        <overview>
            <paragraph id="p1">As everyone does, I too have hobbies and interest that I put my free time into. I would say my main hobby is art.</paragraph>
            <paragraph id="p2">Art can mean different things to different people, but ultimately, anything creative or self-made can be art.</paragraph>
        </overview>
    </introduction>
    <content>
        <definition>
            <description id="d1">Art is all around us and very subjective.</description>
        </definition>
        <personalArt>
            <type name="digital drawing" primary="true">
                <programs>
                    <program name="Pencil2D" years="2017-2018" review="Very simple and easy to use, but lacks functions outside of essentials"/>
                    <program name="FireAlpaca" years="2020-2025" review="Solid, reliable program with all necessities and free to install"/>
                    <program name="IbisPaintX" years="2023-2025" review="Free, easy to use, only available for mobile devices"/>
                    <program name="Procreate" years="2024-2025" review="Good brushes and clean UI, expensive and different from other programs"/>
                </programs>
            </type>
            <community>
                <onlineGroups>Engages in numerous online art communities</onlineGroups>
                <collaboration>Collaborates with friends for art projects</collaboration>
            </community>
            <benefits>
                <mentalHealth>Creative output is therapeutic and inspiring</mentalHealth>
            </benefits>
        </personalArt>
        <aiArt>
            <opinion author="self">AI cannot replace real artists; it lacks soul and emotions.</opinion>
            <discussion>
                <point>AI art makes art more accessible but lacks human creativity</point>
                <point>Artists overcome disabilities to create beautiful works</point>
            </discussion>
        </aiArt>
